import os
import numpy as np
import matplotlib
from  matplotlib import pyplot as plt
import librosa
from ipywidgets import interact, fixed, FloatSlider
import IPython.display as ipd
%matplotlib inline

Fs = 128
duration = 10
omega1 = 1
omega2 = 5
N = duration * Fs
t = np.arange(0, N) * 1 / Fs
t1 = t[:N//2]
t2 = t[N//2:]

x1 = 1.0 * np.sin(2 * np.pi * omega1 * t1)
x2 = 0.7 * np.sin(2 * np.pi * omega2 * t2)
x = np.concatenate((x1, x2))

plt.figure(figsize=(15, 2))
plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
plt.plot(t, x, c='k')
plt.xlim([min(t), max(t)])
plt.xlabel('Time (seconds)')

plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
X = np.abs(np.fft.fft(x)) / Fs
freq = np.fft.fftfreq(N, d=1/Fs)
X = X[:N//2]
freq = freq[:N//2]
plt.plot(freq, X, c='k')
plt.xlim([0, 7])
plt.ylim([0, 3])
plt.xlabel('Frequency (Hz)');
In [2]:
def windowed_ft(t, x, Fs, w_pos_sec, w_len):
    
    N = len(x)
    w_pos = int(Fs * w_pos_sec)
    w_padded = np.zeros(N)
    w_padded[w_pos:w_pos + w_len] = 1
    x = x * w_padded    
    plt.figure(figsize=(15, 2))

    plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
    plt.plot(t, x, c='k')
    plt.plot(t, w_padded, c='r')
    plt.xlim([min(t), max(t)])
    plt.ylim([-1.1, 1.1])
    plt.xlabel('Time (seconds)')

    plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
    X = np.abs(np.fft.fft(x)) / Fs
    freq = np.fft.fftfreq(N, d=1/Fs)
    X = X[:N//2]
    freq = freq[:N//2]
    plt.plot(freq, X, c='k')
    plt.xlim([0, 7])
    plt.ylim([0, 3])
    plt.xlabel('Frequency (Hz)')
    
w_len = 4 * Fs
windowed_ft(t, x, Fs, w_pos_sec=1, w_len=w_len)
windowed_ft(t, x, Fs, w_pos_sec=3, w_len=w_len)
windowed_ft(t, x, Fs, w_pos_sec=5, w_len=w_len)

interact(windowed_ft,
         w_pos_sec=FloatSlider(min=0, max=duration-(w_len/Fs), step=0.1, continuous_update=False, value=1.0),
         t=fixed(t), x=fixed(x), Fs=fixed(Fs), w_len=fixed(w_len));

# definition of stft

def stft(x, w, H=8, Fs=1):
    N = len(w)
    x_pad = np.concatenate((np.zeros(N//2), x, np.zeros(N)))
    start_idx = np.arange(0, len(x), H)

    freq = np.fft.rfftfreq(N, d=1/Fs)
    time = start_idx * 1 / Fs

    X = np.zeros((len(freq), len(start_idx)), dtype='complex')

    for i, idx in enumerate(start_idx):
        x_win = x_pad[idx:idx+N] * w
        X_win = np.fft.rfft(x_win)
        X[:, i] = X_win
        
    return X, freq, time

eps = np.finfo(float).eps
X_db = 10 * np.log10(np.abs(X) + eps)

In [12]:
X = librosa.stft(x, n_fft=64, hop_length=8, window='boxcar')
plt.figure(figsize=(15, 3))
plt.title('centered + "reflect"-padding (default of librosa)')
plt.imshow(np.abs(X), origin='lower', aspect='auto', cmap='gray_r')
plt.ylabel('Index (frequency)')

X = librosa.stft(x, n_fft=64, hop_length=8, window='boxcar', pad_mode='constant')
plt.figure(figsize=(15, 3))
plt.title('centered + zero-padding')
plt.imshow(np.abs(X), origin='lower', aspect='auto', cmap='gray_r')
plt.ylabel('Index (frequency)')

X = librosa.stft(x, n_fft=64, hop_length=8, window='boxcar', pad_mode='constant', center=False)
plt.figure(figsize=(15, 3))
plt.title('non-centered')
plt.imshow(np.abs(X), origin='lower', aspect='auto', cmap='gray_r')
plt.xlabel('Index (frames)')
plt.ylabel('Index (frequency)')
